Incident description

The Indeed.com website experienced a data breach. Almost 30 thousand email addresses were exposed, together with personal, financial and location data. Leaked records include salary, name, phone number and city. The validity of the data exposed couldn’t be verified. Yet we’re still informing you about a potential data breach – but keep in mind there’s a chance of it being a false positive.

                          Job title: Node.JS Developer with Microservices

                          Location: Irving, TX

                          Duration: Long-term

                          Verizon

                          Onsite - Locals will give preference

                          Skill required:

                          • 12+ Year of overall IT Experience
                          • Experience in Telecom Industry is a Must
                          • Hands-on experience in Node.js development.
                          • Strong experience designing and developing microservices.
                          • Strong knowledge and 5+ years of experience with MongoDB.
                          • Hands-on experience with SQL databases (e.g., PostgreSQL, MySQL).
                          • Extensive working experience with Apache Spark for data processing.
                          • Proficiency with RESTful APIs, JSON, and API design standards.
                          • Design, develop, and maintain scalable and high-performing Node.js-based microservices.
                          • Integrate and manage data using MongoDB and SQL databases efficiently.
                          • Implement real-time or batch data processing using Apache Spark.
                          • Write clean, modular, and testable code following best practices.
                          • Participate in code reviews, design discussions, and system architecture planning.
                          • Monitor and debug production systems, ensuring uptime and performance.

                          Job Type: Contract

                          Pay: $50.00 - $55.00 per hour

                          Expected hours: 40 per week

                          Experience:

                          • Node JS Developer: 10 years (Required)
                          • Telecom Industry is a Must: 5 years (Required)
                          • MongoDB.: 6 years (Required)
                          • SQL databases (e.g., PostgreSQL, MySQL): 10 years (Required)
                          • Apache Spark for data processing: 8 years (Required)
                          • RESTful APIs, JSON, and API design standards: 6 years (Required)
